            <title>[LUCENE-716] Support unicode escapes in QueryParser</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-716</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;As suggested by Yonik in &lt;a href=&quot;http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-573&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot;&gt;http://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-573&lt;/a&gt; the QueryParser should be able to handle unicode escapes, i. e. \uXXXX.&lt;/p&gt;

